milestones.description: Fletcher has scored 3 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for ENG breaking John Edrich's record
Fletcher has become the top scorer for ENG in ODIs with 338 runs, going past Dennis Amiss's 322
Mike Denness has broken the record for most ODIs (4) as captain for ENG, going past Brian Close
Syed Abid Ali has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (2) for IND, going past Bishan Bedi
Fletcher and Tony Greig's 59-run partnership is the highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 55 between Vic Pollard and Glenn Turner
Fletcher and Tony Greig's 59-run partnership is ENG's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 48 between Mike Denness and Tony Greig
Sudhir Naik and Gopal Bose's 8-run partnership is IND's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 6 between Ajit Wadekar and Gavaskar
Ajit Wadekar and Gopal Bose's 12-run partnership is IND's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 10 between Ajit Wadekar and Viswanath
Viswanath and Brijesh Patel's 19-run partnership is IND's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 13 between Eknath Solkar and Brijesh Patel
Syed Abid Ali and Ashok Mankad's 14-run partnership is IND's highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 1 between Srinivas Venkataraghavan and Brijesh Patel
This is the lowest match aggregate (343) involving teams England & India in ODIs
Elliott has broken the record for officiating the most ODIs (4) as an umpire, going past Dusty Rhodes
Fletcher has become the top scorer in ODIs with 338 runs, going past Dennis Amiss's 322
